<br>
I do agree with some of your statements though, but for exp groups,, hes going to get owned in PoS and PoV at 60 in Thurg armor with 6aa's.  Maybe he can do flowers, bears and trees in PoS forest but he might as well stay in PoN and do Consorts or butterflys.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I don't think AA's matter that much. Get every buff you possibly can, and with the right group set up and intelligent people<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Well, if there using crappy weapons or have small mana pools they just won't have the DPS to do it, wether there super inteligent people or retards.<br>
<br>
