<br>
Well I always have an enchanter with me, so im a little biased in my camps.  But consorts needs a mezzer or harmony.  There all lvl 60 so exp is much better than LCY or LCR which &quot;suck&quot; for exp anyways.  I just don't think youve seen 1/4 of PoN and PoD if your doing LCY/LCR and thinking that's good exp.  <br>
