<br>
The Key to this is fast Targeting. As MA, you need to switch with about 10% life to next target. I would also suggest having someone shout time. When I flagged a rogue friend we had a Wizard doing this. <br>
<br>
At the start of a round and after each kill he would start a Hotkey. Would say 28 Seconds Left to Kill Target. then 20 Sec, then 15, Then 10, then at about 6 or so he would say... NUKE hard and Kill it we are running out of time. It kept us all focused.<br>
<br>
This helped alot. And we passed it 1st shot. That group was a 61 War, 62 Cleric, 65 Wiz, 65 Ench, 60 Rogue, and a 61 Wiz.<br>
<br>
