<br>
I would suggest you make sure you have Virtue, Focus, Brells. Hell any HP buff that will Stack. Also, Make sure All Melee have a Slow Hotkey and Spam it if you get slowed until it is removed. Several Times, either me or monk/rogue being slowed has caused failure's.<br>
<br>
